@Access_Token = 在这里粘贴通过 OIDC 获取的 access_token
@Second_Access_Token = 可选：在这里粘贴第二个账号的 access_token，用于验证“非发帖者不能开奖”
@Gateway_HostAddress = https://localhost:5000

@Lottery_DrawTime = 在这里填一个晚于当前时间的 RFC3339 时间，例如 2026-03-16T23:59:00+08:00
@ForumLottery_PostId = 在这里填入带抽奖帖子的 postId
@ForumLottery_RootCommentId = 在这里填入参与抽奖的父评论 commentId

### 发布带抽奖帖子
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Post/Publish
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

{
  "title": "论坛抽奖 MVP 验收帖",
  "content": "用于串联论坛抽奖 MVP 验收：列表识别、父评论参与、开奖与中奖名单回显。",
  "categoryId": 1,
  "tagNames": ["抽奖", "验收"],
  "lottery": {
    "prizeName": "Radish 周边礼包",
    "prizeDescription": "包含贴纸、徽章与纪念卡各一份。",
    "drawTime": "{{Lottery_DrawTime}}",
    "winnerCount": 2
  }
}

### 获取带抽奖帖子的列表
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Post/GetList?keyword=论坛抽奖%20MVP%20验收帖&pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 获取带抽奖帖子详情
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Post/GetById/{{ForumLottery_PostId}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 按帖子获取抽奖详情（开奖前）
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Lottery/GetByPostId?postId={{ForumLottery_PostId}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 发布父评论参与抽奖
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Comment/Create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

{
  "postId": {{ForumLottery_PostId}},
  "content": "这是参与抽奖的父评论，用于验证按用户去重统计参与人数。",
  "parentId": null,
  "replyToUserId": null,
  "replyToUserName": null
}

### 对父评论发布回复（预期：不增加参与资格）
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Comment/Create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

{
  "postId": {{ForumLottery_PostId}},
  "content": "这是对父评论的回复，按规则不应计入抽奖资格。",
  "parentId": {{ForumLottery_RootCommentId}},
  "replyToUserId": null,
  "replyToUserName": null
}

### 获取根评论分页，核对父评论层级
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Comment/GetRootComments?postId={{ForumLottery_PostId}}&pageIndex=1&pageSize=20&sortBy=default
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 获取子评论分页，核对回复层级
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Comment/GetChildComments?parentId={{ForumLottery_RootCommentId}}&pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 再次获取抽奖详情（预期：父评论计入，回复不计入）
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Lottery/GetByPostId?postId={{ForumLottery_PostId}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 未到开奖时间时尝试开奖（预期失败）
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Lottery/Draw
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

{
  "postId": {{ForumLottery_PostId}}
}

### 非发帖者尝试开奖（可选，预期失败）
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Lottery/Draw
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Second_Access_Token}}

{
  "postId": {{ForumLottery_PostId}}
}

### 到开奖时间后由发帖者手动开奖
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Lottery/Draw
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

{
  "postId": {{ForumLottery_PostId}}
}

### 开奖后再次获取抽奖详情
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Lottery/GetByPostId?postId={{ForumLottery_PostId}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 开奖后再次获取帖子详情，确认中奖名单与抽奖状态回显
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Post/GetById/{{ForumLottery_PostId}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}
